    "description": "Killbug，欢迎来到昆虫王国的腹地，此处的虫群正为统治地位之争而陷入无尽战争。<br><br>你用你的力量威胁了它们。它们剪掉了你的翅膀，迫使你被放逐，但这还不足以平息它们的怨恨。一场穷凶极恶的埋伏战正在前方等你，它们要的是你的性命。<br><br>刀刃和枪管期待血液的滋味，渴望复仇的甜蜜。<br><br>你会让他们吃尽苦头，而它们，从甲壳到胸节都会感受到痛苦。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >死神降临</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211730/extras/c0df50ddbc3026797696475a4c5126b3.poster.avif?t=1747868841\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211730/extras/c0df50ddbc3026797696475a4c5126b3.webm?t=1747868841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211730/extras/c0df50ddbc3026797696475a4c5126b3.mp4?t=1747868841\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>作为Killbug，在这个残酷的战场上，运用你类似昆虫的直觉去冲刺、连跳和飞檐走壁。综合这些流畅的运动机制，找到地图上所有区域的敌人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >屠杀虫群</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211730/extras/bb8c5a0f664b09a853053a1eeb4b9175.poster.avif?t=1747868841\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211730/extras/bb8c5a0f664b09a853053a1eeb4b9175.webm?t=1747868841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211730/extras/bb8c5a0f664b09a853053a1eeb4b9175.mp4?t=1747868841\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在成群的贪婪野兽之中杀出一条血路。从甲壳虫到蜘蛛，再到巨型幼虫怪兽，有无穷无尽的虫群等着你以Killbug的身份去屠戮。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >杀死轮回</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211730/extras/df868a36acdcf8dcf369a8f2e39d155f.poster.avif?t=1747868841\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211730/extras/df868a36acdcf8dcf369a8f2e39d155f.webm?t=1747868841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2211730/extras/df868a36acdcf8dcf369a8f2e39d155f.mp4?t=1747868841\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>随着不断重生，变成死亡的主人，向敌人降下毁灭，冲向你的下一个高分。碾碎那些虫子，不知疲倦。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 和各色野蛮昆虫战斗。<br></li><li> 在快节奏的残酷战斗中消灭成百上千的虫子。<br></li><li> 用你的刀和冲锋枪砍杀射击敌人。<br></li><li> 利用空中运动原理来实现连跳、近身冲撞、枪械摆动等，快速适应对抗各种敌人的攻击方式。<br></li><li> 在全球排行榜上创造新的高分纪录，或者通过比赛把好友挤下头把交椅。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >辅助功能</h2><br>Killbug包含多种辅助功能，适用于有运动类疾病的玩家。",
